ISLAMABAD, Apr 10 (APP):Minister for Water Resources Faisal Vawda Friday expressed deep grief and sorrow over the demise of Syed Mehdi Shah, brother in law of Chief Minister Syed Murad Ali Shah.
In his condolence message, the minister prayed for the rest of departed soul in eternal peace and grant solace to the bereaved family to bear this irreparable loss with equanimity.
